        {
            "title": "財經｜聯想(03396)悉售東方航空物流持股 套現逾27億人幣",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜聯想(03396)悉售東方航空物流持股 套現逾27億人幣\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/La7gZ15XzW1pdZUwE2YseQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTUwMg--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/fortune_insight_694/dbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜聯想(03396)悉售<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"東方航空\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:東方航空;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/東方航空\">東方航空</a>物流持股 套現逾27億人幣</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯想控股(03396)公布，擬以現金對價27.17億元(人民幣．下同)悉售於上交所上市的東方航空物流的11.29%股權予中國物流資本。完成後，公司不再持有東方航空物流股份。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯想預計，出售事項完成後，公司將確認稅前收益約2.97億元。出售事項將增強公司流動性水平及營運資金，有利於鞏固公司的財務及現金狀況，出售事項所得款淨額擬用於日常營運及或償還債務。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E8%81%AF%E6%83%B3-03396-%E6%82%89%E5%94%AE%E6%9D%B1%E6%96%B9%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E7%89%A9%E6%B5%81%E6%8C%81%E8%82%A1-%E5%A5%97%E7%8F%BE%E9%80%BE27%E5%84%84%E4%BA%BA%E5%B9%A3-010352332.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-04-09 09:13:49",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "品浩據悉擬出售用於興建甲骨文數據中心之140億美元債務融資的一部分",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 知情人士透露，品浩(Pacific Investment Management Co.)尋求出售140億美元債務融資的一部分，該融資是用於在密西根州建設甲骨文的巨型數據中心。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">知情人士透露，位於薩林鎮的這座數據中心將獲得163億美元的融資，其中約15%將以股權投資的形式。這些知情人士因涉及非公開資訊而要求匿名，彭博新聞也看到擬議中的交易條款。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">交易條款顯示，品浩是此次融資的主要出資方，整體交易由美國銀行主導，預計4月17日完成。彭博先前報導稱，黑石集團計劃20億美元的股權投資。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-714f82da-35f7-33ed-abad-86b157de0ca0-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">品浩和美國銀行的發言人都拒絕置評，黑石集團的一名代表尚未立即回應置評請求。甲骨文表示，該公司對其在薩林鎮設施的融資和開發方面取得的「快速進展」感到自豪。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">推薦閱讀：品浩據悉考慮為甲骨文數據中心提供約140億美元的債務融資</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題Pimco Seeks to Sell Parts of $14 Billion Oracle Data Center Debt</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"bloomberg.com\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2026 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
